          "commentType": "FUNCTION",
          "texts": [
            {
              "value": "Participates in both the initiation and recycling phases of transcription. In the presence of the delta subunit, RNAP displays an increased specificity of transcription, a decreased affinity for nucleic acids, and an increased efficiency of RNA synthesis because of enhanced recycling"
            }
          ]
